data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exceptional 6-bedroom, 4-full bathroom & 3-half bathroom single-family residence is a testament to luxurious living and thoughtful design. With a perfect blend of classic charm and contemporary amenities, this move-in-ready home offers a spacious and inviting environment for you and your family. Nestled on the picturesque tree-lined Westchester Blvd, this residence enjoys a prime location, seamlessly blending tranquility with convenience. The property backs up to a community park, providing not only a stunning natural backdrop but also easy access to outdoor activities and leisure. Originally constructed as a two-story Baltis built home, this residence underwent a thoughtful expansion, adding a family room to the main floor and introducing additional living space on the second floor. The result is a sprawling 3797 sq ft above-grade living area, ensuring ample room for every aspect of your lifestyle. The main floor exudes warmth and functionality with a well-designed layout featuring a living room, dining room, eat-in-kitchen, side entrance/mudroom area, family room, and two convenient half baths. The seamless flow from the family room and kitchen to the large deck creates a perfect space for both relaxation and entertainment. Upstairs, the second floor unveils a total of 6 bedrooms, including two with en-suite bathrooms, and 2 more full baths, providing both privacy and comfort for the entire family. The primary bedroom, with its own en suite, adds a touch of luxury to your daily retreat. The lower level of the home is a haven for recreation and relaxation. A finished recreation room boasts a custom wet bar, wood-burning fireplace, half bath, and a practical laundry area. Abundant closets and storage spaces throughout the home cater to your organizational needs. This much-loved home has been meticulously maintained and recently refreshed with numerous quality updates, ensuring a modern and comfortable living experience. Just steps away from the park district and community pool, and mere minutes from major expressways, public transportation, shopping, and restaurants, this property is not just a house; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary residence your new home.
